freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Two days temp. 99.9-100.2.Headache:  3-4 days.Skin sensitivity, burning, slight redness around right chest at both mid/lower thoracic levels; no lesions but feels like herpes zoster. Low back/thigh muscle pain & fatigue walking outside today.
freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: I sent a note describing symptoms to my Infectious Disease doctor.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I did have cataract surgery this morning.
